    "By focusing on the broader aspects of program structure and logic, this activity could prepare students for the complexities of real-world computational scenarios while still harnessing the power of generative AI.LLM-based sequencing activities in other educational contexts.",
    "The concept of sequencing pieces of a solution can be applied to other learning contexts, such as reading, foreign language, and math education [15].",
